{"tid":564442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國有好多自以為國際形勢專家成日睇高美國幾理班","createTime":"2018-02-18T03:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T04:31:52.000Z","uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20bad51e864eb00d4bab8a21e77c86d6fa0ee13b","tid":564442,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"法國有好多自以為國際形勢專家成日睇高美國幾班<br />\n不斷吹美國撚邊個邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實話美國係咁撚狗既國際觀有幾差呢<br />\n單就拎南海單野黎講啦<br />\n初時又話國際仲裁撚中國<br />\n結果人地理都唔撚理你個仲裁<br />\n繼續係南海填島<br />\n最近一次南海既新聞 已經有成年前<br />\n果時跑道起哂 防空導彈都部處哂係果到<br />\n最後菲律賓都埋中國堆<br />\n現實係美國自克林頓以黎<br />\n對於抗衡中國既戰略部署係徹底失敗<br />\n唔明有咩好吹"},{"pid":"cacaabdae90e370573789d8bd8698ec9b3942ce0","tid":564442,"uid":83623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"你又好撚醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中天TVBS 都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94addcc602d8184da0d0374cb2eaebbb9809ce81","tid":564442,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cacaabdae90e370573789d8bd8698ec9b3942ce0","tid":564442,"uid":83623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"你又好撚醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中天TVBS 都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"五毛質素係差啲"},{"pid":"444cad9f8fda20f8fa9811e7da08eff6a860a4c9","tid":564442,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"學識打字先啦你條撚樣 法乜撚野國？"},{"pid":"e7552f836330bfdcbd65f8561db8a3c63e4c2bda","tid":564442,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444cad9f8fda20f8fa9811e7da08eff6a860a4c9","tid":564442